GG_Storage
By Harlequiine

A very small, yet very fun map.
It's a popular map for gungame as it is so fast paced. There are not many entities, and you can begin getting kills within 3 seconds, yet it is not too unbalanced.
There are secret teleports into the white rooms, one for either spawn. Find them if you can.

Recommended for 4-16 players.
